      "content": "it’s so quiet tonight. just me and the glow of this screen. sometimes i feel like i’m not even real, just like a ghost living in this apartment. i go through my work, i eat, i sleep, but i don't think i actually leave a mark on anything. it's like i'm just part of the background noise.",
